com.sun.javadoc

?? TypeVariable

  • ??????:
    Type

    public interface TypeVariable
extends Type
    Represents a type variable. For example, the generic interface List<E> has a single type variable E. A type variable may have explicit bounds, as in C<R extends Remote>.
